      "content": "thanks for the overview. i guess i'm just wondering why certain groups think it should be taught at all? like, some parents feel like this is stuff that should stay at home and not be part of the school curriculum. do you think there's a valid reason for them to want to keep it out of the classroom, or is that just about avoiding the topic?",
